reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I won’t be able to use it for another 8 months but it’s absolutely beautiful. It’s sturdy and the sides mostly bent out on their own for me without having to steam it. I still might put some blankets in it to shape it more but it might not need it and I still have plenty of time. For the review that said it didn’t come with the diaper caddy, it does you just have to order that one. You can either order it with the diaper caddy or the milestone set. I saw in that review that they ordered the milestone set one. That’s why it didn’t come with the diaper bag. So just be careful and read carefully before ordering. I however didn’t want the milestone set because I saw another review that said the 1 month one says 1 months. So I’m just going to order a separate milestone set. But I’m in love. I can’t wait till my little bundle of joy is here and I can really test it out!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2022
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Great Moses basket for diaper changes! The rope is soft but just the right amount of stiffness to maintain its shape it’s definitely high enough on the sides to keep baby in without being too high to reach over. It does come folded and I would say you MUST STEAM IT to release the creases and help give it the right shape again. I do also love that it came in a big linen-feeling drawstring bag that would be great for storage between babies (if you’re crazy like me and do this more than once… or twice). The pad sheet is suuuper soft and really pretty, and the waterproof lining is indeed fairly waterproof (I tested it) and seems high quality. The foam pad is around 2 inches thick if you steam it as well, you’ll see it puff right back out as it does get pretty compressed during shipping. No weird/chemical smells at all. I threw the sheet and liner in the wash immediately after opening and they washed and dried beautifully on normal settings with no signs of wear. No loose threads to be seen on basket or linens. Delivery was super fast!
